        {
            "title": "邁威生物下限27.64元定價  下周二掛牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國製藥公司邁威生物(02493)公布，每股發售價已釐定為27.64元，為招股價下限。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：邁威生物官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250107_FI_source-web_688062.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：邁威生物官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250107_FI_source-web_688062.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：邁威生物官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">邁威生物發售4713.02萬股H股，以此計算，集資約13.03億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股預期下周二(28日)掛牌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">邁威生物招股價介乎27.64港元至30.71港元，集資最多14.5億港元。每手200股，一手入場費約6204港元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中信証券、海通國際為聯席保薦人。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">市場估計，邁威公開招股超額認購297倍，公司發行4713萬股H股，一成於香港作公開發售︱</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以招股範圍計，邁威生物的估值介乎185.9億至187.3億港元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15916717-%e9%82%81%e5%a8%81%e7%94%9f%e7%89%a9%e4%b8%8b%e9%99%9027-64%e5%85%83%e5%ae%9a%e5%83%b9-%e4%b8%8b%e5%91%a8%e4%ba%8c%e6%8e%9b%e7%89%8c",
