            "title": "A股午後跌幅收窄   滬股一周升28點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後跌幅收窄，深股一度重上15000，惟未能穩守，兩市成交合計26418.59億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指全日報4769點，跌16點或0.35%，今早開跌8點或0.19%，報4081點，上午見4061，跌32點或0.78%，為全日低位，午後升破上午高位，報4092點，僅跌1點，全日成交11430億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指全日報14940，挫103點或0.69%，今早開跌92點或0.61%，報14951點，最低見14795，跌248點或1.64%，為全日低位，午後高見15033，僅跌10點或0.06%，全日成交14988.59億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數全日報4769點，跌16點或0.35%，今早開跌15點或0.31%，報4771點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數跌52點或1.41%，報3667點，今早開跌1.02%或38點，報3682點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬骰一周計升28點或0.69%，深股一周升55點或0.36%。</p>\n</div>",
